flowchart LR
    A[Draft object] --> B[Local markdown draft]
    A --> C[Local asset staging]
    B --> D[Preview package]
    C --> D

    D --> E[Telegram group review]
    E -->|not approved| F[revise draft]
    F --> A

    E -->|approved| G[Write repo]
    G --> H[Website publish path]

    X[Important rule] --> D
    X[Preview first\nPublish second]
